ther at Protests, Why Doesn’t He Attend One?</span></h4><div class="Promo-author" data-reactid="305"><!-- react-text: 306 -->Robert Mackey<!-- /react-text --><span class="Promo-date" data-reactid="307"><!-- react-text: 308 --> —<!-- /react-text --><!-- react-text: 309 --> <!-- /react-text --><span data-reactid="310">Apr. 18</span></span></div></div><div class="Promo-excerpt" data-reactid="311"><!-- react-empty: 312 --></div></div></div></a></div></div><div class="Promo-container" data-reactid="313"><div data-reactid="314"></div><div class="Promo Promo--default Promo--video" data-reactid="315"><a class="Promo-link" href="/2020/04/17/coronavirus-fema-trump-misinformation/" data-reactid="316"><div class="GridRow" data-reactid="317"><div class="Promo-image-container" data-reactid="318"><div class="Promo-image-block" data-reactid="319"><div class="ResponsiveImage Promo-image" style="padding-top:50%;" data-reactid="320"><noscript data-reactid="321"><img src="https://theintercept-static.imgix.net/usq/ad5bd1f0-e9a4-401c-8bcd-e0abe9180a77/ad5bd1f0-e9a4-401c-8bcd-e0abe9180a77.bin?auto=compress,format&cs=srgb&dpr=2&h=450&w=900&fit=crop&crop=faces%2Cedges&_=16a9b30fed6a542d57356b4d399e4727" alt="null" class="ResponsiveImage-image" height="900" width="1800"></noscript></div></div></div><div class="Promo-text" data-reactid="322"><div class="PromoVideoPlayButton Promo-playButton Promo-playButton--in-title" data-reactid="323"></div><div class="Promo-title-block" data-reactid="324"><h4 class="Promo-title" data-reactid="325"><span class="Promo-title-wrap" data-reactid="326">FEMA’s Coronavirus Rumor Control Webpage Sidesteps Trump’s Lies</span></h4><div class="Promo-author" data-reactid="327"><!-- react-text: 328 -->Nick Turse<!-- /react-text --><span class="Promo-date" data-reactid="329"><!-- react-text: 330 --> —<!-- /react-text --><!-- react-text: 331 --> <!-- /react-text --><span data-reactid="332">Apr. 17</span></span></div></div><div class="Promo-excerpt" data-reactid="333"><!--